  "description": "Content-to-Pipeline: Turning Content Into Revenue workflow skill. Use this skill when the user needs When the user wants to turn content into revenue, build a content-led GTM motion, reverse engineer distribution, or repurpose content across platforms. Also use when the user mentions 'content marketing,' 'content-led growth,' 'content to pipeline,' 'distribution,' 'content repurposing,' 'content strategy,' 'thought leadership,' 'newsletter,' 'content flywheel,' 'organic growth.' This skill covers content-to-revenue systems from creation through pipeline attribution. Do NOT use for technical implementation, code review, or software architecture and the operator should rely on the packaged workflow, support pack, troubleshooting notes, and provenance links before merging or handing off.",
